Th25: (M1 is  col_circulant implies ( - M1 ) is  col_circulant)
proof
A1: ( Indices M1 ) = [: ( Seg n ),( Seg n ) :] by MATRIX_1:24;
A2: ( Indices ( - M1 ) ) = [: ( Seg n ),( Seg n ) :] by MATRIX_1:24;
